# ── Per-agent Agentverse Mailbox Keys ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://agentverse.ai → My Agents → New Agent → Local Agent
# Create one agent per row below, copy the "Agent Mailbox Key" shown after creation.
# Each key looks like: eyJ0...very_long_base64_string...
